lead_paragraph: Liverpool manager Juergen Klopp will drop any player he feels is showing signs of complacency in the side's assault on the Premier League title but the German remains confident that none of his squad are taking anything for granted.

headline.print_headline: Klopp Warns Against Complacency at Title-Chasing Liverpool
